-- China Stock Trading Account Openings Falls 57% From Week Ago to 111,948
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-22T22:41:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/china-stock-trading-account-openings-falls-57-from-week-ago-to-111-948.html

          
          
             Investors opened 57 percent fewer
accounts for trading Chinese stocks during the week ended June
18 as compared with the previous week, according to the China
Securities Depository and Clearing Corp.  
 Investors opened 111,948 accounts during the week,
according to the clearing house.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
